title: The OutZeiters 10/29: Nickelodeon, Jack Nicklaus, Halloween, Miracle Whip
itunes:title: The OutZeiters 10/29: Nickelodeon, Jack Nicklaus, Halloween, Miracle Whip
description:
On this edition of the OutZeiters Jack and Miles discuss Nickelodeon's "Presidential Election for Kids" being hacked by 4Chan, Jack Nicklaus has endorsed Donald Trump, there are many clever devices being made to distribute candy, and the debate between Mayo and Miracle Whip on a sandwich...rages on Twitter?
